Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.64,0:00:04.08,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"En Doji Hiramune, un psicòleg criminalista...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.16,0:00:07.08,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"que havia adreçat un seguit de provocacions a un assassí en sèrie,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.16,0:00:09.56,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"autor d'uns crims que estan a punt de prescriure,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.64,0:00:11.64,Yellow,,0,0,0,,ha estat assassinat a casa seva."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.68,0:00:15.12,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"A l'esquena l'assassí li ha marcat una Z."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.40,0:00:20.80,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Al cos sense vida de les altres 3 víctimes de l'assassí en sèrie,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.96,0:00:24.80,Yellow,,0,0,0,,s'hi van trobar marcades les lletres E, S i W."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.88,0:00:27.20,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Això, afegit al fet que la Haibara i l'Ayumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.28,0:00:28.88,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"han vist un sospitós que xiulava,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.96,0:00:30.84,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"ha permès a la policia determinar
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.92,0:00:33.00,Yellow,,0,0,0,,que és un nou crim de l'assassí en sèrie."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.48,0:00:36.60,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"He acompanyat l'inspector Takagi,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.68,0:00:39.28,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"que anava a interrogar les famílies de les víctimes anteriors,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.36,0:00:42.40,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"i m'he adonat que el nexe que tenen en comú les 4 víctimes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.48,0:00:44.20,Yellow,,0,0,0,,és el mahjong."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.96,0:00:47.96,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Descobriré la veritable identitat de l'assassí en sèrie
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.04,0:00:49.76,Yellow,,0,0,0,,costi el que costi!"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.32,0:00:52.80,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"L'amor és etern. Els misteris, un laberint."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.88,0:00:55.20,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Preparats per trobar-ne la sortida?"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.28,0:00:57.08,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Un parany per un inspector Takagi entusiasmat."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.48,0:00:59.48,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"L'amor i el cas fan un gir inesperat."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.56,0:01:01.36,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"La veritat sempre s'acaba sabent."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.44,0:01:04.92,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Sembla un nen però té el cervell d'un adult i és el detectiu Conan!"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.28,0:01:09.32,Songs,,0,0,0,,Konna nimo soba ni iru noni Boku no omoi todokanakute.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.64,0:01:12.28,Songs,,0,0,0,,Tokei no hari wa makimodosenai.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.40,0:01:18.84,Songs,,0,0,0,,Tomo ni mita ano keshiki wo Wasureshimawanai youni.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.24,0:01:24.80,Songs,,0,0,0,,Kioku no pazuru wo atsumete toumeina kimi no hitomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.16,0:01:30.00,Songs,,0,0,0,,Utsuru sugata ano koro no boku janai keredo.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.00,0:01:33.72,Songs,,0,0,0,,Everlasting love.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.00,0:01:37.64,Songs,,0,0,0,,Meikyuu no youni meguru sekai de
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.00,0:01:41.28,Songs,,0,0,0,,kawaranai omoi wo kimi ni...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.60,0:01:43.28,Songs,,0,0,0,,Everlasting love.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.36,0:01:46.56,Songs,,0,0,0,,Ima wa mada ienai keredo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.92,0:01:50.44,Songs,,0,0,0,,kimi dake wo aishiteru. Everlasting love.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.56,0:01:54.20,Songs,,0,0,0,,Ichido dake negai ga kanau nara
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.52,0:01:57.84,Songs,,0,0,0,,Kaeritai kimi no tonari ni.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.20,0:01:59.88,Songs,,0,0,0,,Everlasting love.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.96,0:02:03.28,Songs,,0,0,0,,Subete no nazo wo tokiakashite
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.44,0:02:07.52,Songs,,0,0,0,,Kimi to zutto zutto irareru youni.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.20,0:02:12.32,Songs,,0,0,0,,Tsunaida sono te wo hanasanai kara.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.92,0:02:17.32,Songs,,0,0,0,,Yume no naka de kimi ni sasayaita.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.92,0:02:21.36,Songs,,0,0,0,,Itsuka kanarazu mukae ni yuku yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.92,0:02:24.92,Songs,,0,0,0,,Everlasting love.
